{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Common Ground · An open standard for sovereign Indigenous data platforms · OIATC{% endblock %}
{% block description %}First Nations are building their own data platforms one at a time, and none of them can work together yet. Common Ground is an open standard OIATC is starting now: a shared way for sovereign platforms to exchange data, enforce each Nation's rules, and prove they follow them. An early open call to take part.{% endblock %}
{% block body_class %}route-standards-common-ground{% endblock %}

